        <h4 class="nomination-name"><a href="?nomination=4c58-tweeting-truth:-al-jazeera-english-s-2022-coverage-on-twitter">Tweeting Truth: Al Jazeera English’s 2022 Coverage on Twitter</a></h4>
    </div>
    <div class="nomination-info">
                

                
    
    
    
    <div class="nomination-qa Textbox doc">
        <div class="nomination-qu">Company or team name</div>
        
        
        <div class="nomination-an">AJE Social Teams</div>
        


        

