        <div class="nomination clearfix list has-custom has-showhide" id="nomination-ddb112bd-3a64-4415-a612-512df4810a7d" data-slug="3a64-he-was-my-high-school-journalism-teacher-then-i-investigated-his-relationships-with-teenage-girls" data-winnerclass="Award" style="display: none">

