        <h4 class="nomination-name"><a href="?nomination=e944-revitalizing-connections:-a-brave-new-look-for-a-global-community">Revitalizing Connections: A Brave New Look for a Global Community</a></h4>
    </div>
    <div class="nomination-info">
                

                
    
    
    
    <div class="nomination-qa Textbox doc">
        <div class="nomination-qu">Company or team name</div>
        
        
