        <div class="nomination-an">Lara O’Reilly has become the go-to journalist for highly readable yet in-depth news on advertising and how it impacts consumers, small businesses, and major companies. She is easily able to parse technical stories for a general business audience. And her unique approach to covering the industry through a tech-first lens has been prescient, in that it has enabled her to break stories on the companies that act as the internet’s economic engine, such as Apple and Meta. Her sources tell her: You write the stories no one else is writing.</div>
        


        

