This was the case for our MINI Electric partnership: with our Haymarket Automotive Studio team taking a handful of raw influencer-style assets created directly by MINI, and enriching, expanding and amplifying them into a comprehensive multi-channel native content campaign that delivered above and beyond expectations to far exceed MINI’s KPIs for reach, engagement and sentiment change.</div>
        


        

